description: Everyone in OKC just can’t get enough of the wonderfully delicious gourmet donuts from Metro Minis. These cute little cake donut delights are hot, fresh, and made to order. You just choose which made-from-scratch toppings you’d like. Their selection includes Sunshine (drizzle of lemon glaze with blueberry puree), Spotted Elk (drizzle of chocolate and caramel with a dash of sea salt), Cinnamon Sugar, Cookies & Cream, and so much more. With these unforgettably tasty treats and sincerely sweet service, Metro Minis are  simply a must-have at your next party or event.
name: Metro Minis OKC
